flowchart TD
    A[Incoming Client Request] --> B[FastAPI Gateway]
    B --> C[Fetch Healthy and Enabled Backends]
    C --> D{Any Eligible Backends?}

    D -- No --> E[Return 503 Service Unavailable]
    D -- Yes --> F[Load Static Backend Weights]

    F --> G[Add Static Weight to Each Current Score]
    G --> H[Select Backend with Highest Current Score]
    H --> I[Subtract Total Active Weight from Selected Backend Score]
    I --> J[Forward Request to Selected Backend]

    J --> K{Backend Response Successful?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Return Response to Client]
    K -- No --> M{Retry Attempts Remaining?}

    M -- No --> N[Return Final Error Response]
    M -- Yes --> O[Exclude Failed Backend]
    O --> P{Another Eligible Backend Available?}

    P -- No --> N
    P -- Yes --> C

    L --> Q[Record Selected Backend and Weight]
    N --> Q
    Q --> R[Persist Request and Attempt Data in Supabase]
    R --> S[Publish Live Request Lifecycle Events]
    S --> T[Update Real-Time API Request Topology]

    U[Example Weights] --> U1[Fast Backend: 5]
    U --> U2[Slow Backend: 2]
    U --> U3[Unstable Backend: 1]
    U1 --> V[Expected Long-Term Ratio: 5 to 2 to 1]
    U2 --> V
    U3 --> V
